  selectFolder: (options?: { title?: string; defaultPath?: string }) =>
    ipcRenderer.invoke(IPC_CHANNELS.DIALOG_SELECT_FOLDER, options),
}
```

### Options
- `title`: Dialog window title (default: "Select Folder")
- `defaultPath`: Initial directory to display (useful for showing current vault path)
- `properties`: `openDirectory` (folders only), `createDirectory` (allow new folder button)

### Return Value
- `string`: Absolute path to selected folder
- `null`: User cancelled the dialog

